'''Wakkerstroom''' ke toropo go feta [[Pixley ka Seme Mmusogae]], [[Mmasepala Setereke tša Gert Sibande]] wa diporofense [[Mpumalanga]] kamoka [[Afrika Borwa]].

Toropo ke hleng la [[KwaZulu Natala]] border, 27 km bohlabela ya [[Volksrust]] le 56 km borwa-bohlabela ya [[Amersfoort, Mpumalanga|Amersfoort]].

